(48, 1, '2015-07-05 23:48:44', '2015-07-05 23:48:44', 'By providing high quality workplace health assessments, Alere are able to identify, target and improve health risks for individuals as well as your entire workforce.\r\n\r\nAt Alere, we understand that due to variations in age, gender and personal medical history, a â€˜one size fits allâ€™ approach to health isnâ€™t ideal.\r\n\r\nTo cater for the broad range of employee health needs, Alere has developed a range of flexible health assessment options. We design your program to meet the needs of your organisation, and further tailor each health assessment to the needs of individual staff members.\r\n\r\nThese health assessment options are delivered by our experienced and fully qualified team and our cholesterol analyser has been certified by the Cholesterol Reference Method Laboratory Network (CRMLN) for its accuracy and reproducibility compared to laboratory results. Our health assessment components include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Blood Pressure, Cholesterol &amp; Glucose</li>\r\n	<li>HbA1c Testing for diabetes risk NEW!</li>\r\n	<li>Bone Density Screening</li>\r\n	<li>Vision &amp; Glaucoma Screening</li>\r\n	<li>Hearing Screening</li>\r\n	<li>Skin Cancer Risk Assessment</li>\r\n	<li>Stress, Anxiety &amp; Depression</li>\r\n	<li>Weight Management</li>\r\n	<li>Fitness &amp; Strength Testing</li>\r\n	<li>Back &amp; Core Testing</li>\r\n	<li>Posture &amp; Flexibility Assessment</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur Health Assessment options range from <a href="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/services/online-health-programs/online-health-risk-assessments/">online health risk assessments</a> or a 10 minute health check, to comprehensive medical assessments.\r\n\r\n<a href="mailto:info@smghealth.com.au">Contact our team</a> today for more information.', 'Health Assessments', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'health-assessments', '', '', '2015-07-07 03:09:10', '2015-07-07 03:09:10', '', 46, 'http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/?page_id=48', 0, 'page', '', 0),
