(50, 1, '2015-07-05 23:48:55', '2015-07-05 23:48:55', 'Corporate flu vaccinations are a cost-effective method of avoiding the suffering of influenza. Studies have shown that employees who have had a flu vaccination experienced a 90% reduction in the risk of contracting influenza and 44% fewer visits to their GP1.\r\n\r\nWith over 20 years of industry experience, Alere provides high quality, best practice corporate flu vaccination programs. Benefits of our corporate flu vaccinations include:\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>flu vaccinations can be delivered nationally and onsite</li>\r\n<li>professional service and flu vaccination program management</li>\r\n<li>dedicated flu vaccination coordinators</li>\r\n<li>innovative marketing support</li>\r\n<li>convenient online booking system</li>\r\n<li>guaranteed supply of flu vaccination vaccines</li>\r\n<li>cold chain management compliance with flu vaccinationsâ€™ safety management practices</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\nProtect your employees, your community and the productivity of your company with corporate flu vaccinations.\r\n\r\n<p><sub>1<sup></sup>Nicol KL et al. The effectiveness of vaccination against influenza in healthy, working adults. New England Journal of Medicine 1995: 333: 889-893</sub></p>', 'Flu Vaccinations', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'flu-vaccinations', '', '', '2015-07-06 07:47:05', '2015-07-06 07:47:05', '', 46, 'http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/?page_id=50', 0, 'page', '', 0),
