(75, 1, '2015-07-06 00:10:22', '2015-07-06 00:10:22', 'Alereâ€™s Weight Loss Challenge can help your workforce address the high costs associated with overweight and obese staff.\r\n\r\nAlereâ€™s Weight Loss Challenge is an 8 to 12 week competition which creates a supportive and competitive environment for your workforce. The program is based on small, achievable lifestyle changes that deliver both short term success and sustainable results.\r\n\r\nThe program is facilitated by a Qualified Exercise Physiologist with specialised Health Coaching and Weight Loss training. It includes:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Small groups competing as a team</li>\r\n	<li>A 30 page Weight Loss â€˜Empowerâ€™ Book</li>\r\n	<li>Face to face and phone based coaching sessions to maintain motivation</li>\r\n	<li>Team progress meetings</li>\r\n	<li>Customised weekly facts sheets, tips and recipes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="mailto:info@smghealth.com.au">Contact our team</a> for more information.</p>', 'Weight Management', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'weight-management', '', '', '2015-07-07 03:06:49', '2015-07-07 03:06:49', '', 71, 'http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/?page_id=75', 0, 'page', '', 0),
