(79, 1, '2015-07-06 00:10:47', '2015-07-06 00:10:47', '<strong> Ergonomic Assessments</strong>\r\nAlereâ€™s Ergonomic Workstation Assessments provide employees with an understanding of their individual work practices and the changes necessary to decrease their risk of injury and improve productivity. A strong emphasis is placed on postural education, work patterns and pause break advice.\r\n\r\n<strong>Work Movement Analysis</strong>\r\nBy observing workers on the job, our qualified health professionals provide suggested improvements around job design and hazards as well as task-specific, manual handling and warm-up advice.\r\n\r\n<strong>Manual Handling Training</strong>\r\nAlereâ€™s Manual Handling training provides guidance on work base tasks in an interactive workshop. A Work Movement Analysis is ideally undertaken before commencing any Manual Handling Training to ensure the training is specific and relevant for the work group.\r\n\r\n<strong>Warm-up for work</strong>\r\nThese sessions provide stretches and warm up exercises relevant to the specific manual tasks performed by the work group. A â€˜train the trainerâ€™ empowers staff while focusing on specific warm-ups directly prior to high risk tasks.\r\n\r\n<p><a href="mailto:info@smghealth.com.au">Contact our team</a> for more information.</p>', 'Injury Prevention', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'injury-prevention', '', '', '2015-07-07 03:06:29', '2015-07-07 03:06:29', '', 71, 'http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/?page_id=79', 0, 'page', '', 0),
