(239, 1, '2015-07-06 06:51:38', '2015-07-06 06:51:38', 'Welcome to SMG Health. We are a quality health management company (formerly Alere Health Management), now integrating physical and mental health services to provide workplaces with holistic health solutions aimed at enhancing wellbeing and productivity. A 2013 stress and wellbeing survey indicated that almost one in five Australians reported that current stress was having a strong impact on their physical health. In the same survey it was reported that this was impacting negatively in the workplace across a range of critical productivity criteria. This situation had deteriorated from surveys done in previous years. The reciprocal impact of mental health and physical health issues are now unequivocal. The need to provide integrated services to workplaces has never been more important. Over the forthcoming months we will be developing a range of new and exciting services to meet our charter: healthier and more productive workplaces. Watch this space. ', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '34-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-06 06:51:38', '2015-07-06 06:51:38', '', 34, 'http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/34-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
