(244, 1, '2015-07-06 07:24:50', '2015-07-06 07:24:50', '\r\n<p>By providing high quality workplace health assessments, Alere are\r\n  able to identify, target and improve health risks for individuals as\r\n  well as your entire workforce.<br> </p>\r\n <p>At Alere, we understand that due to variations in age, gender and\r\n  personal medical history, a â€˜one size fits allâ€™ approach to health\r\n  isnâ€™t ideal.<br> </p>\r\n <p>To cater for the broad range of employee health needs, Alere has\r\n  developed a range of flexible health assessment options. We design\r\n  your program to meet the needs of your organisation, and further\r\n  tailor each health assessment to the needs of individual staff\r\n  members.<br> </p>\r\n <p>These health assessment options are delivered by our experienced and\r\n  fully qualified team and our cholesterol analyser has been certified\r\n  by the Cholesterol Reference Method Laboratory Network (CRMLN) for its\r\n  accuracy and reproducibility compared to laboratory results. Our\r\n  health assessment components include:</p>\r\n <ul> <li>\r\n    <i>Blood Pressure, Cholesterol &amp; Glucose</i></li> <li>\r\n    <i>HbA1c Testing for diabetes risk NEW!<br> </i></li> <li>\r\n    <i>Bone Density Screening</i></li> <li>\r\n    <i>Vision &amp; Glaucoma Screening</i></li> <li>\r\n    <i>Hearing Screening</i></li> <li>\r\n    <i>Skin Cancer Risk Assessment</i></li> <li>\r\n    <i>Stress, Anxiety &amp; Depression</i></li> <li>\r\n    <i>Weight Management</i></li> <li>\r\n    <i>Fitness &amp; Strength Testing</i></li> <li>\r\n    <i>Back &amp; Core Testing</i></li> <li>\r\n    <i>Posture &amp; Flexibility Assessment</i></li> </ul>\r\n <p>Our Health Assessment options range from <a href="/au/en/health-solutions/health-management/online-wellness-tools/online-hra.html#rightpar_shadedbox_fe0e">online\r\n    health risk assessments</a> or a 10 minute health check, to\r\n  comprehensive medical assessments.</p>\r\n <p>\r\n  <a href="mailto:au.enquiries@alere.com">Contact our team</a> today for\r\n  more information.</p>\r\n\r\n', 'Health Assessments', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '48-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-06 07:24:50', '2015-07-06 07:24:50', '', 48, 'http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/48-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
