(339, 1, '2015-07-07 02:53:25', '2015-07-07 02:53:25', 'Welcome to SMG Health. We are a quality health management company (formerly Alere Health Management), now integrating physical and mental health services to provide workplaces with holistic health solutions aimed at enhancing wellbeing and productivity. A 2013 stress and wellbeing survey indicated that almost one in five Australians reported that current stress was having a strong impact on their physical health. \r\n\r\nIn the same survey it was reported that this was impacting negatively in the workplace across a range of critical productivity criteria. This situation had deteriorated from surveys done in previous years. The reciprocal impact of mental health and physical health issues are now unequivocal. The need to provide integrated services to workplaces has never been more important. Over the forthcoming months we will be developing a range of new and exciting services to meet our charter: healthier and more productive workplaces.', 'SMG Health', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '132-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-07 02:53:25', '2015-07-07 02:53:25', '', 132, 'http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/132-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(340, 1, '2015-07-07 03:06:12', '2015-07-07 03:06:12', 'Alere has a variety of Health Portal options to suit your organisational needs and budget.\r\n\r\n<strong>Health Resource Centre</strong>\r\n\r\nAlereâ€™s Health Resource Centre comes with extensive health information and self-managed health programs to provide your staff with the knowledge and skills to improve their health. The Health Resource Centre also includes Alereâ€™s Online Health Risk Assessment.\r\n\r\n<strong>Comprehensive Online Health Portal</strong>\r\n\r\nAlereâ€™s Online Health Portal includes:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Health Risk Assessment (HRA)</li>\r\n	<li>Online Booking System</li>\r\n	<li>Health Resources including fact sheets and healthy recipes</li>\r\n	<li>Self-Managed Health Programs</li>\r\n	<li>Health Calculators &amp; Quizzes</li>\r\n	<li>Regular e-newsletters</li>\r\n	<li>Reporting â€“ Access to real time de-identified data on the health of your staff</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="mailto:info@smghealth.com.au">Contact our team</a> for more information.</p>', 'Portals & Programs', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '83-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-07 03:06:12', '2015-07-07 03:06:12', '', 83, 'http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/83-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(341, 1, '2015-07-07 03:06:29', '2015-07-07 03:06:29', '<strong> Ergonomic Assessments</strong>\r\nAlereâ€™s Ergonomic Workstation Assessments provide employees with an understanding of their individual work practices and the changes necessary to decrease their risk of injury and improve productivity. A strong emphasis is placed on postural education, work patterns and pause break advice.\r\n\r\n<strong>Work Movement Analysis</strong>\r\nBy observing workers on the job, our qualified health professionals provide suggested improvements around job design and hazards as well as task-specific, manual handling and warm-up advice.\r\n\r\n<strong>Manual Handling Training</strong>\r\nAlereâ€™s Manual Handling training provides guidance on work base tasks in an interactive workshop. A Work Movement Analysis is ideally undertaken before commencing any Manual Handling Training to ensure the training is specific and relevant for the work group.\r\n\r\n<strong>Warm-up for work</strong>\r\nThese sessions provide stretches and warm up exercises relevant to the specific manual tasks performed by the work group. A â€˜train the trainerâ€™ empowers staff while focusing on specific warm-ups directly prior to high risk tasks.\r\n\r\n<p><a href="mailto:info@smghealth.com.au">Contact our team</a> for more information.</p>', 'Injury Prevention', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '79-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-07 03:06:29', '2015-07-07 03:06:29', '', 79, 'http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/79-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(342, 1, '2015-07-07 03:06:49', '2015-07-07 03:06:49', 'Alereâ€™s Weight Loss Challenge can help your workforce address the high costs associated with overweight and obese staff.\r\n\r\nAlereâ€™s Weight Loss Challenge is an 8 to 12 week competition which creates a supportive and competitive environment for your workforce. The program is based on small, achievable lifestyle changes that deliver both short term success and sustainable results.\r\n\r\nThe program is facilitated by a Qualified Exercise Physiologist with specialised Health Coaching and Weight Loss training. It includes:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Small groups competing as a team</li>\r\n	<li>A 30 page Weight Loss â€˜Empowerâ€™ Book</li>\r\n	<li>Face to face and phone based coaching sessions to maintain motivation</li>\r\n	<li>Team progress meetings</li>\r\n	<li>Customised weekly facts sheets, tips and recipes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="mailto:info@smghealth.com.au">Contact our team</a> for more information.</p>', 'Weight Management', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '75-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-07 03:06:49', '2015-07-07 03:06:49', '', 75, 'http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/75-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(343, 1, '2015-07-07 03:07:11', '2015-07-07 03:07:11', 'Alere runs the worldâ€™s largest and most successful smoking cessation program, having helped over one million people quit smoking and contributing to over 100 scientific journal articles. The program has a workplace smoking cessation quit rate of 47%1 and has proven highly successful in Australia.\r\n\r\nAlereâ€™s Free and Clear<sup>Â®</sup>programs include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A consistent national service</li>\r\n	<li>Group behaviour therapy</li>\r\n	<li>Personalised coaching</li>\r\n	<li>Pre &amp; post <a href="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/services/onsite-health-services/health-assessments/">Health Assessments</a></li>\r\n	<li>Video-conferencing option for remote locations</li>\r\n	<li>Discounted Nicotine replacement therapy</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href="mailto:info@smghealth.com.au">Contact our team</a> for more information.\r\n\r\n<sup>1 </sup><a href="http://www.alerewellbeing.com/quit-for-life"><sup>www.alerewellbeing.com/quit-for-life</sup></a>', 'Smoking Cessation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '73-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-07 03:07:11', '2015-07-07 03:07:11', '', 73, 'http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/73-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(344, 1, '2015-07-07 03:07:31', '2015-07-07 03:07:31', '<b>Gym Management</b>\r\n\r\nManaging some of the countryâ€™s leading corporate gymnasiums, Alere provides all facets required to establish a successful onsite fitness facility.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Design</li>\r\n	<li>Equipment &amp; Maintenance</li>\r\n	<li>Staffing &amp; Management</li>\r\n	<li>Group Exercise &amp; Fitness Programs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>Fitness Classes</b>\r\n\r\nAlere provides a variety of on-site fitness classes as either a one off session or delivered as an ongoing program. These include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Aerobic Circuits</li>\r\n	<li>Strength Circuits</li>\r\n	<li>Yoga</li>\r\n	<li>Pilates</li>\r\n	<li>Boxing</li>\r\n	<li>Boot Camp</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href="mailto:info@smghealth.com.au">Contact our team</a> for more information.', 'Gym Management & Fitness Classes', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '58-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-07 03:07:31', '2015-07-07 03:07:31', '', 58, 'http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/58-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(345, 1, '2015-07-07 03:07:57', '2015-07-07 03:07:57', 'Health expos are a cost and time effective way to showcase health in the workplace. Every Alere Health Expo is designed specifically to suit your workforce and business needs.\r\n\r\nOur expos are a fun way to maximise the reach of your workplace wellness program and engage those staff who are traditionally the last to participate. Alereâ€™s Health Expos can include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Innovative <a href="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/services/onsite-health-services/health-assessments/">Health &amp; Wellness Assessments</a></li>\r\n	<li>Cooking Demonstrations and food &amp; smoothie tastings</li>\r\n	<li>15-30 minute Health Seminars</li>\r\n	<li>Neck &amp; Shoulder Massage</li>\r\n	<li>Individual Counselling on Physical Activity, Nutrition, Weight Management &amp; Smoking Cessation</li>\r\n	<li>Resources and information on all relevant heath topics</li>\r\n	<li>Competitions, show bags, door prizes and healthy give-aways</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="mailto:info@smghealth.com.au">Contact our team</a> for more information.</p>', 'Health Expos', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '56-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-07 03:07:57', '2015-07-07 03:07:57', '', 56, 'http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/56-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(346, 1, '2015-07-07 03:08:43', '2015-07-07 03:08:43', 'Each year more than 400,000 Australians undergo treatment for skin cancer, with more than 11,500 cases of Melanoma diagnosed <sup>1</sup>. In 2011 there were more than 2000 deaths due to Skin Cancer<sup>1</sup>\r\n\r\nAlere offer programs that can:\r\n\r\n<ol> <li>Detect suspicious lesions</li>\r\n<li>Identify individuals at high risk</li> \r\n<li>Encourage employees to regularly check their skin</li> </ol>\r\n\r\n<strong>Skin Cancer Screening</strong>\r\nAlere has performed skin checks to over 50,000 patients Australia wide â€“ including checks in every state and territory, in every capital city, and in hundreds of regional and remote locations. Experienced and skilled General Practitioners conduct thorough skin checks on-site and make immediate recommendations on treatment and follow-up actions.\r\n\r\n<strong>Skin Cancer Risk Education</strong>\r\nAlere use an evidence-based risk prediction tool to provide an individual risk of developing a melanoma. Participants are provided with their individual risk rating and education on sun safety practices. Participants also view the sun damage to their skin using a specialised lamp designed to highlight the importance of regular self-checks. The Skin Cancer Risk Assessment can be incorporated into a more comprehensive Health Assessment.\r\n\r\n<p><a href="mailto:info@smghealth.com.au">Contact our team</a> for more information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><sup>1 Cancer Council 2013, </sup><a href="http://www.cancer.org.au/policy-and-advocacy/position-statements/sun-smart/"><sup>http://www.cancer.org.au/policy-and-advocacy/position-statements/sun-smart/</sup></a></p>', 'Skin Cancer Screening', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '52-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-07 03:08:43', '2015-07-07 03:08:43', '', 52, 'http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/52-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(347, 1, '2015-07-07 03:09:10', '2015-07-07 03:09:10', 'By providing high quality workplace health assessments, Alere are able to identify, target and improve health risks for individuals as well as your entire workforce.\r\n\r\nAt Alere, we understand that due to variations in age, gender and personal medical history, a â€˜one size fits allâ€™ approach to health isnâ€™t ideal.\r\n\r\nTo cater for the broad range of employee health needs, Alere has developed a range of flexible health assessment options. We design your program to meet the needs of your organisation, and further tailor each health assessment to the needs of individual staff members.\r\n\r\nThese health assessment options are delivered by our experienced and fully qualified team and our cholesterol analyser has been certified by the Cholesterol Reference Method Laboratory Network (CRMLN) for its accuracy and reproducibility compared to laboratory results. Our health assessment components include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Blood Pressure, Cholesterol &amp; Glucose</li>\r\n	<li>HbA1c Testing for diabetes risk NEW!</li>\r\n	<li>Bone Density Screening</li>\r\n	<li>Vision &amp; Glaucoma Screening</li>\r\n	<li>Hearing Screening</li>\r\n	<li>Skin Cancer Risk Assessment</li>\r\n	<li>Stress, Anxiety &amp; Depression</li>\r\n	<li>Weight Management</li>\r\n	<li>Fitness &amp; Strength Testing</li>\r\n	<li>Back &amp; Core Testing</li>\r\n	<li>Posture &amp; Flexibility Assessment</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur Health Assessment options range from <a href="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/services/online-health-programs/online-health-risk-assessments/">online health risk assessments</a> or a 10 minute health check, to comprehensive medical assessments.\r\n\r\n<a href="mailto:info@smghealth.com.au">Contact our team</a> today for more information.', 'Health Assessments', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '48-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-07 03:09:10', '2015-07-07 03:09:10', '', 48, 'http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/48-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
