itute of Chartered Accountants - Australia\r\n  Chartered Institute of Management Accountants - UK\r\n  Association of Accounting Technicians â€“ UK </i> Twenty five years of work experience in diversified organisations (Public listed, SMEs) which includes <a href="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/team-5.png"><img class="img-thumbnail img-responsive alignright wp-image-383 size-thumbnail" src="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/team-5-150x150.png" alt="" width="150" height="150" /></a>Manufacturing, Stock broking, Real Estate, Financial services, Employee Wellness and Other Professional service sectors as a Senior Member and Head of Finance.\r\n  \r\n  Worked for A4e Group of Companies as the Finance Director (CFO) and Company Secretary since March 2013. Prior to the above role, worked as the CFO, Director for PPC Worldwide for 11 years (A United Health Group Company, NYSE entity). Key roles included Overseeing all financial activities (whilst overseeing a team) that entailed budgeting, forecasting, month-end reporting, audit, tax, procurement, ERP implementation, mergers and acquisitions. A key part of the role involved aligning finance closely with the business to assist with company performance / activities, strategic direction and business growth. </div>\r\n<div class="col-md-12 sen_me_tem">\r\n  <h2>Tim</h2>\r\n  <i> Senior Commercial Account Manager </i> Tim is an Exercise Physiologist with a post graduate qualification in Health Promotion. Over the last 15 yea<a href="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/team-4.png"><img class="img-thumbnail img-responsive alignright wp-image-379 size-thumbnail" src="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/team-4-150x150.png" alt="" width="150" height="150" /></a>rs he has designed and managed some of Australiaâ€™s largest and most successful workplace wellness programs. Over the last decade Tim has presented regularly at industry conferences in the areas of Best Practice and Return on Investment in workplace wellness. In his current role as Senior Commercial Account Manager, he is the responsible for the program design and relationship management for major clients throughout Australia and New Zealand as well as the management of SMGâ€™s Commercial Team.â€\r\n  \r\n  Title is tricky. Technically current title is â€œCommercial Account Managerâ€. However I want to differentiate my title from CAM, so it carries more weight with clients when issues get escalated â€“ so I have been unofficially using â€œSenior Commercial Account Managerâ€. As background, when Birgit (previous â€˜Health Management MDâ€™ then â€˜Strategic Relationships Managerâ€™) went on Mat leave â€“ I was given higher duties but no title change. Her role was made redundant but this has never been formally announced so had no impact on org structure or my official role / title. My current role includes duties within CAM, Strategic Relationships Manager and Health Management Business Manager.\r\n  \r\n  Suggestions below but Im happy with any title that fits within org structure so let me know your preference and Il use it from July 1st.\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>Senior Commercial Account Manager</li>\r\n    <li>National Commercial Manager</li>\r\n    <li>National Relationships Manager</li>\r\n    <li>Business Manager</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'Senior Management Team', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '334-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-07 04:53:53', '2015-07-07 04:53:53', '', 334, 'http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/334-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
