(429, 1, '2015-07-07 08:50:24', '2015-07-07 08:50:24', '<div class="col-md-12">\r\n  <p class="text-justify">SMG Health (formerly Alere Health Management) is a Corporate Health Provider consisting of a skilled and passionate multidisciplinary team of health professionals committed to the enhancement of organisation health and productivity. SMG brings a professional team with over 20 yearsâ€™ experience providing corporate health services with a strong  focus on mental health across the Asia Pacific region. The addition of this expertise aligned with the existing skills and excellence in service of the Alere Health Management team ensures that this further evolution of the Company will provide companies in Australia and indeed across the APAC with cutting edge holistic health solutions. These solutions will be available through various platforms and service mediums (on-line, face to face and telephonic) tailored specifically the needs of the organisation.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<row>\r\n\r\n  <div class="col-md-6 m_t1  "> <img src="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/brond-vistion.png" alt="brond-vistion" width="558" height="195" class="img-thumbnail img-responsive m_b1"/> </div>\r\n  <div class="col-md-6 m_t1  ">\r\n    <h2>Brand Vision</h2>\r\n    <p class="text-justify ">SMG Health is committed to the enhancement of organisational health and well-being leading to improved individual organisational performance and productivity through the provision of high quality holistic health services across the Asian Pacific region.</p>\r\n  </div>\r\n</row>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6 ">\r\n  <h2>Who is SMG Health?</h2>\r\n  <p class="text-justify ">SMG Health is the health management company that delivers connected holistic health services.</p>\r\n\r\n    <ul class="list-inline right_arrow text-justify">\r\n      <li>it stems from the unique way we connect health data and health management solutions. That connectivity provides the timely and actionable information essential to making better health decisions</li>\r\n      <li>No other health management company provides the same degree of  holistic health information because no other company connects the whole person through focussed mental, physical, behavioural and social products and services spanning a capability across all organisations</li>\r\n      <li>Our services are designed from a bespoke platform to meet specific organisational needs</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n \r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6  ">\r\n  <h2>Our Promise</h2>\r\n  <p class="text-justify ">SMG Health connects critical health data and health management solutions to enable timely and actionable information that drives organisational health well-being and productivity.</p>\r\n  <h2>Our Approach</h2>\r\n  <p class="text-justify ">The SMG Health approach to organisational health and well-being is striking in its simplicity. We believe, and the evidence indicates, that healthy well balanced employees are more productive employees who remain with their employer for a longer time, with reduced absenteeism, presenteeism, and workers compensation premiums thereby creating a strong base for higher levels of engagement, productivity and retention of expertise and experience. Our integrated holistic health solutions using both physical and mental health service platforms and connecting compelling health data with our services means SMG Health assists you in achieving these desired workplace outcomes.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n<row>\r\n  <div class="col-md-6 "> <img src="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/why_are_we_different.png" alt="why_are_we_different" width="558" height="195" class="img-thumbnail img-responsive"  /> </div>\r\n  <div class="col-md-6 ">\r\n    <h2>Why are we different? </h2>\r\n    <p class="text-justify "><strong>Holistic Connected Health</strong></p>\r\n    <p class="text-justify " >Whether itâ€™s setting up a wellness program or managing a chronic condition, we at SMG Health know that the key to good health is access to timely and actionable information. By actively connecting diagnostics and health management solutions, SMG Health gives decision-makers (Individual employees and organisations) the tools they need to make informed health and well-being choices. The result? Weâ€™re empowering people and organisations by providing a pathway to enhanced well-being and productivity</p>\r\n  </div>\r\n</row>\r\n<div class="col-md-12 m_t1">  <h2>Our Senior Team</h2></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n<div class="our_senio_section">\r\n<div class="col-md-2 m_t1">\r\n<img src="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/team-2-150x150.png" alt="team-2" width="150" height="150" class="img-thumbnail img-responsive" />\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-2 m_t1">\r\n<img src="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/imageIan-150x150.jpg" alt="imageIan" width="150" height="150" class="img-thumbnail img-responsive" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-2 m_t1">\r\n<img src="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/team-1-150x150.png" alt="team-1" width="150" height="150" class="img-thumbnail img-responsive" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-2 m_t1">\r\n<img src="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/team-5-150x150.png" alt="team-5" width="150" height="150" class="img-thumbnail img-responsive" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-2 m_t1">\r\n<img src="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/team-4-150x150.png" alt="team-4" width="150" height="150" class="img-thumbnail img-responsive" />\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n <a href="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/company/senior-management-team/" target="_blank" class="text-center">Read More</a>\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '20-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-07 08:50:24', '2015-07-07 08:50: