 wellness program or managing a chronic condition, we at SMG Health know that the key to good health is access to timely and actionable information. By actively connecting diagnostics and health management solutions, SMG Health gives decision-makers (Individual employees and organisations) the tools they need to make informed health and well-being choices. The result? Weâ€™re empowering people and organisations by providing a pathway to enhanced well-being and productivity</p>\r\n  </div>\r\n</row>\r\n<div class="col-md-12 m_t1">  <h2>Our Senior Team</h2></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n<div class="about_senior_team">\r\n<div class="col-md-2 col-md-13 m_t1">\r\n<img src="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/team-2-300x300.png" alt="team-2"  class="img-thumbnail img-responsive" />\r\n<p  class="team_tytle">Brian Meltzer</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-2 col-md-13 m_t1">\r\n<img src="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/team-3-300x300.png" alt="imageIan"  class="img-thumbnail img-responsive" />\r\n<p  class="team_tytle">Ian Shakespeare</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-2 col-md-13 m_t1">\r\n<img src="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/team-1-300x300.png" alt="team-1"  class="img-thumbnail img-responsive" />\r\n<p  class="team_tytle">Jaqui Bond</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-2 col-md-13 m_t1">\r\n<img src="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/team-5-300x300.png" alt="team-5"  class="img-thumbnail img-responsive" />\r\n<p  class="team_tytle">Philomina Gunasekera</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-2 col-md-13 m_t1">\r\n<img src="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/team-4-300x300.png" alt="team-4"  class="img-thumbnail img-responsive" />\r\n<p  class="team_tytle">Tim Nelson</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-12 "><a href="http://111.93.163.213/SMGHealth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/team-4-300x300.png" class="about